<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">No. It is more like three books with the same theme. One does not build on the other. (Note that I am reading them in order, and I have not yet read T<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">No. It is more like three books with the same theme. One does not build on the other. (Note that I am reading them in order, and I have not yet read The Human Stain.)<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
